            <h2>About Us</h2>
            <p class="content">
                At Adopt-A-Dog, we believe that every dog deserves a loving home. Founded in 2024, our mission is to help rescue dogs 
                find their forever families. We work closely with shelters and foster homes to provide a safe haven for dogs in need. 
                Our dedicated team ensures that every dog is matched with the right family based on their personality, needs, 
                and preferences.
            </p>
            <p class="content">
                We are passionate about giving dogs a second chance and educating the public on responsible pet ownership. 
                Whether you're looking to adopt a puppy or an older dog, we offer a variety of dogs ready to bring joy into your home. 
                Our goal is to ensure a smooth adoption process that makes both dogs and owners happy.
            </p>
        </section>


